{"data":{"actions":[{"callId":"chatcmpl-tool-a9c61f4eb688e230","input":{"filename":"recruiting_resume_screener_report.md","title":"Prioritized Action Report – Recruiting Resume Screener","markdown":"# Prioritized Action Report – Recruiting Resume Screener\n\n**Context**\n- Dossier loaded for the Recruiting resume screener (Agent ID: 29‑recruiting‑resume‑screener).\n- Operational analysis of recent records completed (limit = 10).\n\n**Key Records (sorted by impact & risk)**\n| ID | Title | Status | Impact | Risk | Opportunity |\n|----|-------|--------|--------|------|--------------|\n| 29‑A | Recruiting resume screener priority case | **Urgent** | **51,193** | 6 (high) | 7 |\n| 29‑C | Recruiting resume screener blocked follow‑up | Blocked | 24,119 | 4 (moderate) | 2.4 |\n| 29‑B | Recruiting resume screener routine queue item | In Review | 12,277 | 3 (low) | 1.2 |\n\n**Prioritization Rationale**\n1. **Urgent high‑impact case (29‑A)** – Largest impact and elevated risk; aligns directly with the core mission of fair resume screening.\n2. **Blocked follow‑up (29‑C)** – Substantial impact but stalled by a cross‑functional dependency; removing the block would unlock significant opportunity.\n3. **Routine queue item (29‑B)** – Lower impact and risk; can be addressed after the two higher‑priority items.\n\n**Recommended Actions**\n- **Activate case 29‑A**: Assign reviewer resources, verify fairness guardrails, and deliver a recommendation within 24 hours.\n- **Unblock case 29‑C**: Identify the responsible stakeholder (e.g., legal or data‑privacy), hold a brief triage meeting (≤ 30 min), and document the resolution path.\n- **Proceed with case 29‑B**: Schedule a 2‑hour slot after the urgent case is resolved, applying the same fairness checklist used for 29‑A.\n\n**Assumptions & Uncertainties**\n- Impact figures are internal monetary equivalents; exact conversion may vary.\n- No protected‑class attributes are considered; all decisions use job‑related criteria only.\n- Availability of cross‑functional partners for the blocked case is assumed within the next business day.\n\n**Next Steps**\n- Communicate this prioritized plan to the recruiting operations lead.\n- Track progress in the task system, updating each record’s status accordingly.\n- Re‑run `analyze_records` after 48 hours to reassess risk/opportunity shifts.\n\n*Report generated from loaded dossier and analyzed records.*"},"kind":"tool-call","toolName":"write_report"}],"sequence":0,"stepIndex":4,"turnId":"turn_0"},"type":"actions.requested","meta":{"at":"2026-06-18T15:19:04.790Z"}}
